Materials:

-Rail Guides. like "Igus" (http://www.igus.es/wpck/6189/filmtechnology)
-Camera Ball and Socket Tripod Head
-Stepper motor NEMA 17
-Aluminium pulley GT2.
-GT2 timing belt 6mmx2m
-EasyDriver (https://www.sparkfun.com/products/12779)
-Arduino Micro
-PowerBoost 1000 Charger - Rechargeable 5V Lipo USB Boost(https://www.adafruit.com/products/2465)
-Potenciometer
-3 bottoms
-wire
-608zz Axial Bearing x2
-Female DC Power adapter Jack.
-Bluetooth (Bluefruit EZ-Link), I used this, but you can use any other. HC-05

You can power the arduino with LiPo battery
and feed the driver + Motor nema with 8 AA batteries holder case .
